DOC.brief_summary: To demonstrate the relative bioequivalency of Cord's 100 mg Desipramine HCl tablets to Merrell Dow's 100 mg Norpramin tablets.
DOC.brief_title: To Demonstrate the Relative Bioequivalency of Cord's 100 mg Desipramine HCL Tablets To Merrell Dow's 100 mg Norpramin Tablets
DOC.criteria: No clinically significant abnormal finding on physical exam, medical history, or clinical laboratory results on screening. Positive test results for HIV or hepatitis B or C. Treatment for drug or alcohol dependence.
